708
00:33:51,980 --> 00:33:52,930
historical data.

709
00:33:52,930 --> 00:33:54,900
Again, we're a
statistical agency.

710
00:33:54,900 --> 00:33:57,900
So we're really looking
carefully at the data.

711
00:33:57,900 --> 00:33:59,900
But it can take some
