00:47:10,130 --> 00:47:12,830
And we're going to work
really hard on documentation

1012
00:47:12,830 --> 00:47:14,720
so people can understand
what we're doing.

1013
00:47:14,720 --> 00:47:18,163
We want it to be robust so
that we can capture uncertainty

1014
00:47:18,163 --> 00:47:20,080
and that we have insights
that are conditioned

1015
00:47:20,080 --> 00:47:21,640
on that uncertainty.

